text: Janez Mlinar was a cross-country skier from Yugoslavia. Mlinar competed at the 1968 Winter Olympics. He was born on 14 August 1941 and died in 2020.Janez Mlinar == References == Category:1941 births Category:2020 deaths Category:Skiers Category:Olympians for Slovenia Category:Olympians for Yugoslavia
